# Components & Animation

## Header

Fixed top. Left: "AEDIFICIUM" wordmark. Right: PLATFORM | BRAND LIBRARY | OS | PARTNER LOGIN + REQUEST ACCESS pill. Mobile: hamburger.
Scroll: transparent → `rgba(10,8,6,0.85)` + backdrop-blur via Framer Motion `useScroll` + `useTransform` (no scroll listeners). REQUEST ACCESS: `var(--accent)` bg, dark text.

## Hero

Full viewport, 55/45 split. Left: eyebrow, H1 with italic accent "everything", subtext, two CTAs. Right: masonry 5–6 photos with warm overlay, stagger from right. Background `--bg-base`, optional warm radial glow bottom-left.

## Brand Marquee

Three rows, alternating directions, ◆ separator, 30–40s loop, text only (no images), CSS animation, `animation-play-state: paused` on hover.

## Platform stats

`300+` / `1` / `0` — large number + label, no card border, CountUp on scroll into view.

## Scroll reveal (FadeIn)

```tsx
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 24 }}
  whileInView={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
  viewport={{ once: true, amount: 0.2 }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.7, ease: "easeOut" }}
>
```

Stagger: `staggerChildren: 0.10`, item `y: 20`, duration 0.7 easeOut.

## Hydration-safe client state

```tsx
const [active, setActive] = useState(-1);
useEffect(() => { setActive(0); }, []);
```

## Reduced motion (required)

```tsx
const shouldReduce = useReducedMotion();
const variants = {
  hidden: shouldReduce ? { opacity: 1 } : { opacity: 0, y: 20 },
  visible: { opacity: 1, y: 0 },
};
```
